Open Verse Challenge! Win £1000 worth of studio time with #OldSpiceBars challenge. Duet this video on Tik Tok and upload your verse by 22nd November for a chance of winning.

The winner will be chosen by @oldspiceuk and announced on 25th November by @oldspiceuk and contacted via DM. 

*18+ UK only (excl. CI). Internet access & TikTok account required. Open from 17:00 on 08/11/24 to 23:59 on 21/11/24. To enter, record and post a duet with either @officialchipcm or @djagonline’s challenge launch video to TikTok. Entrants must rap to the ‘Big Man Ting’ instrumental and use the ‘Big Man Ting’ instrumental sound on TikTok. 1 winner will receive a voucher for £1,000 studio time, with DJ AG attending the first studio session for a max of 3 hours. Dates for studio time to be decided in future. Max one entry per person per day. Winner will be chosen by Old Spice after the closing date. By posting their duet, the entrant grants permission for the following accounts to repost their entry on Instagram and TikTok: @oldspiceuk @officialchip @officialchipcm @djagonline. The winner will be announced on @officialchip and @djagonline’s Instagram on 22/11/24 and contacted via direct message on TikTok or Instagram the same day. Old Spice UK is owned by Procter & Gamble, a limited company registered in England and Wales under company number 00083758.

Creating the music video/ad for @oldspiceuk x @officialchip 

Old Spice as a brand have some legendary ads so it was great to have the opportunity to deliver a project like this alongside the team.

Also haven’t caught up with Chip since 2020 so was good to reconnect on this one 🫡

Check out the official video on Chip’s YouTube channel!
